<img src="http://newsroom.uts.edu.au/sites/default/files/styles/wide_landscape/public/images/article_feature/UTS_UMAG_MAR18--8457.jpg?itok=v3s4SGpY" width="980" height="480" alt="Photo of Georgina Barratt-See and Len Tay by Shane Lo" title="Georgina Barratt-See and Len Tay. Photo by Shane Lo" /></div>
